## How a week ends up here

- Only `chore:` / `style:` / `refactor:` (no logic) commits
- Fewer than 3 commits and none of them are `feat:` / architectural
- Only dependency bumps
- Documentation-only weeks

If you disagree with a classification (e.g., a "boring" week actually had
an important pivot that didn't show in commit messages), move the entry
manually to `INTERESTING_WEEKS.md` and add notes there. The next
`/blog timeline` run will respect your manual placement.

